'''Adhi'''
[[File:Hausziege_04.jpg|thumb|Adhi.]]

'''Adhi''' sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''Ari''' ([[Ingiriis]]: Goats) waa [[xoolo]] [[gurijoog]] ah oo [[dad]]ku dhaqdaan. 
Adhigu waa [[xoolo]] [[naasley]] ah, kuwaas oo [[ubuc]]da hoose ku leh [[naas|labo naasood]] oo soo laga helo [[caano]]. 

Adhiga kiisa [[lab]] waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[Orgi]], halka mida [[dhedig]] lagu magacaabo [[Ri']]. Adhigu markuu yaryahay labka waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[neyl]], mida dhedigna waa [[waxar]]. 

[[File:Goat_in_arms.jpg|thumb|Ilmaha adhiga waxa loo yaqaanaa [[neyl]]o iyo [[waxar]]o.]]

Inkastoo ay jiraan in ka badan 300 oo nooc oo adhi ah, hadana xoolaha ugu dhow adhiga ee qaraabada dhow yihiin waxa ka mid ah[[ido|idaha]], adhiga duurjoogta ah iyo sagaarada. 

[[File:Grenadine_Goat_and_Kids.jpg|thumb|[[Ri']] iyo labo ilmo adhi ah: [[waxar]] iyo [[neyl]].]]

Wakhti imika laga joogo [[qarni|10,000]] oo sano ka hor, ayaa wadanka [[Iiraan]] lagu dhaqan jirey adhiga, laakiin waxaa la aaminsan yahay in wakhti intaas ka badan ka hor [[dad]]ku dhaqan jirey adhiga. 
Sida la sheego, dadkii ugu hooreeyay [[beer|wax beerida]] ayaa carbistey adhigii ugu horeeyay sababtoo ah [[caano|caanaha]], [[hilib]]ka, [[dhogor]]ta iyo [[timo|timaha]] hargaha oo laga sameeyo [[dhar]], [[laf]]aha ooy u isticmaali jireen [[adke|adeeygeeda]], [[saxaro|digada]] oo [[caro|carada]] lagu nafaqeeyo ayaa muhiim u ahaa dadkaas beeraleyda ah. 

